summary: Hey everybody, I’m a little strapped for cash and the moment and could really use the extra money. College doesn’t pay for...
caption:
Hey everybody, I’m a little strapped for cash and the moment and could really use the extra money. College doesn’t pay for itself unfortunately. 

So I figured I would open these $10 sketch/doodle commissions in an attempt to make some extra cash. If you could afford it and like my art, I would really appreciate anybody who could help me out by commissioning me. 

The only things I really won’t draw are nudity/nsfw, gore, and and super mechanical things. Thanks everybody!

If you want to see more of my art you can check my art tag or go to my art blog: razzuldazzul.tumblr.com. Send me a message on either account if you’re interested!
